testcase.name: loginWithValidLoginCredentials
testcase.system-out: The driver has launched the website using url : https://www.saucedemo.com The text present on the LoginPage is as same as the expected_text : Swag Labs The driver has entered the username into the text field meant for entering the Username The driver has entered the password into the text field meant for entering the Password The driver has clicked on the Login-Button driver has waited due to ImplicitWait after clicking on the Login-Button The driver has now reached the HomePage hence it is clear that Login was successful The text present on the HomePage is as same as the Expected_text i.e. : Products The driver has navigated to the Menu_Bar and clicked over it The driver has clicked on the Logout-Button. driver has waited due to ImplicitWait after clicking on the Logout-Button The driver has now reached back to the LoginPage now hence it is clear that the Logout was successful
